Vmaxinfo Instituteprovide software testing services and quality assurance services for desktop and mobile applications, to drive quality to your product. Our testing experts work directly with your team to create an end-to-end process that works consistently and rapidly while providing you dedicated support and seamless feedback. Our services are directed to help you achieve quality at speed and ensure that you have a secure online existence.
We also help in Automate the process of testing using Automation Testing Service using Selenium IDE and Webdriver.
Vmaxinfo Institutedeliver corporate training for I.T. indusstries in Software Testing which enhance skill of executives in testing.
